STATE
v.
Delauno Montrez COREY. No. 539PA05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 19, 2006. Robert C. Montgomery, Assistant Attorney General, Seth Edwards, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th day of July 2006 by Defendant to Dissolve Stay:

"Motion Dismissed as Moot by order of the Court in conference this the 19th day of December 2006."
